{"url":"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/staff/5102","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ja\">\n<head>\n<title>弾丸ひとり旅in広島 | アルプ薬局 ブログ</title>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1\">\n\n<!-- All in One SEO Pack 2.3.12 by Michael Torbert of Semper Fi Web Design[40,69] -->\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/staff/5102\" />\n<!-- /all in one seo pack -->\n<link rel='dns-prefetch' href='//ajax.googleapis.com' />\n<link rel='dns-prefetch' href='//s.w.org' />\n<link rel='stylesheet' id='style-css'  href='https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/style.css?ver=4.7.3' type='text/css' media='all' />\n<script type='text/javascript' src='http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js?ver=4.7.3'></script>\n<link rel='shortlink' href='https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/?p=5102' />\n\n<link rel=\"pingback\" href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/xmlrpc.php\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"//fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/notosansjapanese.css\">\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/mplus1p.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" />\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/js/touch.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/js/tabmenu.js\"></script>\n<link rel=\"apple-touch-icon-precomposed\" href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/webclip.png\" />\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/alp.ico\">\n<!--[if lt IE 9]>\n<script src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/js/respond.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/js/html5.js\"></script>\n<![endif]-->\n\n</head>\n\n<body>\n\t\n<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->\n<script async src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-Y3YBPRXKL3\"></script>\n<script>\n  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];\n  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\n  gtag('js', new Date());\n\n  gtag('config', 'G-Y3YBPRXKL3');\n</script>\n<div id=\"wrapper\">\n\n<header id=\"site-header\" role=\"banner\">\n\t\n\n<div class=\"site-title\"><h1><a href=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp\" rel=\"home\"><img src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/logo.png\" width=\"180\"  alt=\"アルプ薬局\"></a></h1></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"blog-title\"><h2>スタッフブログ</h2></div>\n<div class=\"blog-title2\"><p>アルプスタッフがつぶやく、日々の徒然日記</p></div><div class=\"blog-title-img\"><img src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/alp-blog-01.jpg\"></div>\n\n\n\n\n</header>\n\n<div id=\"content\">   \n\n\t<div class=\"post\"> \n<div class=\"post-single\">\n\t\t\n\t\t<div id=\"breadcrumb\">\n        <span class=\"bread\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://data-vocabulary.org/Breadcrumb\"><a href=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/\" itemprop=\"url\"><span itemprop=\"title\">TOP</span> </a></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<span class=\"bread\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://data-vocabulary.org/Breadcrumb\"> <a href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/category/staff\" itemprop=\"url\"><span itemprop=\"title\">スタッフブログ</span></a></span>\t\t</div>\n\n\n<article itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Article\" role=\"main\">\n\n<header>\n<h1 itemprop=\"headline\">弾丸ひとり旅in広島</h1>\n<div class=\"align-right\"><p><i class=\"fa fa-calendar\"></i> <time itemprop=\"datePublished\" datetime=\"2026-04-05T09:00:50+00:00\">2026/04/05</time></p></div>\n</header>\n\n\n<div itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n<div>\n<p>当初の予定が<strong>急遽変更</strong>になって、ぽっかりと空いた✨<strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600\">長めのお休み✨</span></strong>……</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">そうだ！ひとり旅に行こう！&#x1f389;</span></strong></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p>というわけで、先日<strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600\">ほぼ思いつき</span></strong>で（笑）&#x1f600;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">弾丸ひとり旅&#x1f685;</span></strong>へ行ってきました～&#x1f38a;</p>\n<p>2泊3日、行き先は<strong><span style=\"color: #008000\">広島県&#x1f5fe;</span></strong>です。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>初日は新幹線や在来線を乗り継ぎ、<strong>フェリー&#x1f6a2;</strong>で<strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000\">【宮島】</span></strong>へ！！</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5105\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260223_142128-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260223_142128-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260223_142128.jpg 675w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"gmail_chip gmail_drive_chip\">\n<p><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1knbADr9gnfWmqioDNShXFgoS2q5LGZ_L\" target=\"_blank\"><span dir=\"ltr\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5106\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260223_124358-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260223_124358-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260223_124358.jpg 675w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></span></a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"gmail_chip gmail_drive_chip\">\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5107\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260223_133407-1-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260223_133407-1-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260223_133407-1.jpg 675w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"gmail_chip gmail_drive_chip\">\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5108\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260223_145737-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260223_145737-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260223_145737.jpg 675w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600\">参拝＆食べ歩き♡&#x1f60b;&#x1f366;⛩️</span></strong></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div>\n<div class=\"gmail_chip gmail_drive_chip\">\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5109\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260223_140503-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260223_140503-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260223_140503.jpg 675w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #993300\">鹿さん</span></strong>も可愛かったな～&#x1f600;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>2日目は<strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">【原爆ドーム】</span></strong>と<strong><span style=\"color: #008000\">【広島平和記念資料館】</span></strong></p>\n<p>どちらも<strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600\">修学旅行以来の2度目の訪問</span></strong>です&#x1f3c3;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5110\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260224_104631-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260224_104631-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260224_104631.jpg 675w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1c7N-2eFAbDbkGyfGnvpYjTbGsUT2IBkM\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5111\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260224_131400-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260224_131400-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260224_131400.jpg 675w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>実際に足を運び、</strong></p>\n<p>改めていろいろと<strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">考えさせられました&#x1f3e6;</span></strong></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div>\n<p>この日の<strong><span style=\"color: #008000\">広島グルメ</span></strong>は<strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600\">『お好み焼き』&#x1f44f;&#x1f38a;</span></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5112\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260224_142805-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260224_142805-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260224_142805.jpg 675w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></p>\n<p>せっかくなので<strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000\">人気店</span></strong>へ！&#x1f3c3;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600\">ボリューミーでウマウマ～♡</span></strong>&#x1f60b;✨</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>最終日は<strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">【尾道】</span></strong>へ&#x1f3c3;</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5113\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260225_113048-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260225_113048-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260225_113048.jpg 675w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1SQvuAVZVFm9WpRQFcr9C4xZd7u0bR_cD\" target=\"_blank\"><span dir=\"ltr\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5114\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260225_115626-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260225_115626-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/20260225_115626.jpg 675w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></span></a></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"gmail_chip gmail_drive_chip\">\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>人気店の<strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">『尾道ラーメン』&#x1f35c;</span></strong>と、</p>\n<p>可愛くて映えまくりの<span style=\"color: #ff00ff\"><strong>『クレープ』&#x1f353;</strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000\">おいしくて大満足！！</span></strong>&#x1f60b;&#x1f38a;</p>\n<p>しっかり<strong>腹パンです✨&#x1f60b;</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>前日に行き先を決めるという</p>\n<p><strong>完全なる思いつき＆ほぼほぼ食べてばっかりの（笑）&#x1f601;</strong></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"gmail_chip gmail_drive_chip\">\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">弾丸ひとり旅✨&#x1f5fe;&#x1f6a2;&#x1f685;</span></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>しっかり<strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600\">リフレッシュ</span></strong>できました&#x1f44d;</p>\n<p><strong>次はどこに行こうかな～&#x1f3c3;✨</strong></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>富山　N</p>\n<div></div>\n<div class=\"blog-alp-logo\"><img src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/alp-logo.jpg\" width=\"130\" alt=\"アルプ薬局\"></div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"ninja_onebutton\">\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n//<![CDATA[\n(function(d){\nif(typeof(window.NINJA_CO_JP_ONETAG_BUTTON_2e525997ea6182d4250a7da41cf17aa6)=='undefined'){\n    document.write(\"<sc\"+\"ript type='text\\/javascript' src='\\/\\/omt.shinobi.jp\\/b\\/2e525997ea6182d4250a7da41cf17aa6'><\\/sc\"+\"ript>\");\n}else{\n    window.NINJA_CO_JP_ONETAG_BUTTON_2e525997ea6182d4250a7da41cf17aa6.ONETAGButton_Load();}\n})(document);\n//]]>\n</script><span class=\"ninja_onebutton_hidden\" style=\"display:none;\">https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/staff/5102</span><span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"ninja_onebutton_hidden\">弾丸ひとり旅in広島</span>\n</div>\n<br />\n\n</article>\n\n\t\n        </div>\n        <!--/post--> \n\t</div>  \n  </div>\n\n\n<footer id=\"footer\">\n\n<p>Copyright&copy; 2026 ALP Inc. 